<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 08:10:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈马斯的新中东梦想破灭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/hamas-puts-paid-to-dreams-of-a-new-middle-east/0000018b-41b8-d242-abef-53bebaf90000</link><description>只要伊朗不介入冲突，世界经济就能应对以色列最近战争的影响</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 07:48:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/hamas-puts-paid-to-dreams-of-a-new-middle-east/0000018b-41b8-d242-abef-53bebaf90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队：哈马斯知道火箭袭击了加沙医院；拜登即将登陆进行闪电访问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-live/israeli-army-blames-islamic-jihad-for-hitting-gaza-hospital-in-deadly-strike/0000018b-40a6-d881-abab-edae5c5d0000</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登在加沙医院爆炸造成数百人死亡后抵达以色列 ■ 真主党宣布针对以色列的“前所未有的愤怒日” ■ 约旦取消与美国、埃及、巴勒斯坦领导人的峰会 ■ 哈马斯向以色列城市发射火箭弹，以色列国防军称进行了数十次袭击加沙空袭 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,300 名以色列人死亡 ■ 哈马斯：3,200 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，约 11,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 04:12:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-live/israeli-army-blames-islamic-jihad-for-hitting-gaza-hospital-in-deadly-strike/0000018b-40a6-d881-abab-edae5c5d0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对以色列的拥抱使他走上了与阿拉伯世界发生冲突的道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/bidens-embrace-of-israel-sets-him-on-a-collision-course-with-the-arab-world/0000018b-3f5e-dcae-afaf-7ffef5730000</link><description>美国总统对以色列的全力支持以及他全权授权以色列在加沙地带开展行动，这使得他的政府与邻国阿拉伯国家发生冲突，这些国家担心战争可能蔓延到他们的领土</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 03:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/bidens-embrace-of-israel-sets-him-on-a-collision-course-with-the-arab-world/0000018b-3f5e-dcae-afaf-7ffef5730000</guid></item><item><title>作为战争努力的全面合作伙伴，美国寻求保护以色列免受敌人和自身的侵害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/american-wants-to-defend-israel-from-its-enemies-and-itself/0000018b-3f5e-dcae-afaf-7ffee7170000</link><description>美国的努力是巨大的，但美国人对以色列抱有期望，主要是希望以色列国防军向他们表明，他们已经从灾难中恢复过来。总统身边的人也对后天感兴趣</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 03:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/american-wants-to-defend-israel-from-its-enemies-and-itself/0000018b-3f5e-dcae-afaf-7ffee7170000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-4093-d881-abab-ed9be3410000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 02:27:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-4093-d881-abab-ed9be3410000</guid></item><item><title>在对以色列进行史无前例的战区访问时，拜登面临着与时间的赛跑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/on-unprecedented-warzone-visit-to-israel-biden-faces-a-race-against-time/0000018b-4047-df22-a5eb-497fc9ca0000</link><description>随着加沙地带人道主义灾难的发生、以色列和黎巴嫩边境的紧张局势以及阿拉伯领导人取消与他的会晤，美国总统的目标和行程迅速变化</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 01:13:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/on-unprecedented-warzone-visit-to-israel-biden-faces-a-race-against-time/0000018b-4047-df22-a5eb-497fc9ca0000</guid></item><item><title>“决心采取行动”：国会领导人承诺犹太组织全力支持以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/resolved-to-act-congressional-leaders-promise-jewish-groups-full-backing-for-israel/0000018b-4011-d242-abef-52372a5d0000</link><description>参议院多数党领袖查克·舒默誓言美国对以色列的紧急援助计划将“尽快”在