item><title>以色列公众应该受到指责，而不是内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-israeli-public-is-to-blame-not-netanyahu/0000018b-3ed6-d242-abef-7ef6991b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 21:20:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-israeli-public-is-to-blame-not-netanyahu/0000018b-3ed6-d242-abef-7ef6991b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将无法逃脱指责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-wont-be-able-to-escape-blame/0000018b-3ed6-d242-abef-7ef6971b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 21:09:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-wont-be-able-to-escape-blame/0000018b-3ed6-d242-abef-7ef6971b0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登为何访问战时以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/why-biden-is-visiting-wartime-israel/0000018b-3ef6-d2b8-a7db-feff186c0000</link><description>在明确谴责哈马斯恐怖活动后，美国总统拜登带着重要的政治和道德资本抵达以色列。但美以议程上仍有敏感问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 19:32:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/why-biden-is-visiting-wartime-israel/0000018b-3ef6-d2b8-a7db-feff186c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列计划撤离黎巴嫩边境附近社区，许多人拒绝离开</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-plans-to-evacuate-communities-close-to-border-with-lebanon-many-refuse-to-leave/0000018b-3ef7-df22-a5eb-3fff57f10000</link><description>据《国土报》调查，居住在这些社区的 27,000 名居民中，约有 15,000 人仍留在家中。预计他们中的大多数人将很快被疏散，并被送往由以色列政府支付费用的酒店和宾馆</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 19:22:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-plans-to-evacuate-communities-close-to-border-with-lebanon-many-refuse-to-leave/0000018b-3ef7-df22-a5eb-3fff57f10000</guid></item><item><title>消防员从 7,500 英里外接听以色列的紧急呼叫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-firefighters-answering-israels-emergency-call-from-7-500-miles-away/0000018b-3e66-d2b8-a7db-fe6fb67a0000</link><description>与美国志愿者一起度过一个下午，在以色列中部灭火和追赶火箭弹。目前驻扎在拉姆勒的一名加州消防员表示，“这与我在美国经历过的任何事情都不一样”</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 19:14:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-firefighters-answering-israels-emergency-call-from-7-500-miles-away/0000018b-3e66-d2b8-a7db-fe6fb67a0000</guid></item><item><title>“他写信给我：我的父母去世了，我需要帮助”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-17/ty-article-podcast/he-wrote-me-my-parents-are-dead-i-need-help/0000018b-3e82-d2b8-a7db-feef48080000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 19:05:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-17/ty-article-podcast/he-wrote-me-my-parents-are-dead-i-need-help/0000018b-3e82-d2b8-a7db-feef48080000</guid></item><item><title>让以色列在过度拥挤的条件下关押安全囚犯的法案获得初步批准</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/bill-to-let-israel-hold-security-prisoners-in-overcrowded-conditions-gets-initial-approval/0000018b-3ed5-df22-a5eb-3ffd52930000</link><description>该法案将赋予国家安全部长 Itamar Ben-Gvir 豁免居住空间要求的权力，并让囚犯睡在地板上的床垫上</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 18:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/bill-to-let-israel-hold-security-prisoners-in-overcrowded-conditions-gets-initial-approval/0000018b-3ed5-df22-a5eb-3ffd52930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列称伊斯兰圣战组织火箭发射失败，导致加沙医院数百人死亡；哈马斯指责以色列国防军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/hundreds-killed-in-israeli-airstrike-on-gaza-city-hospital-gaza-health-ministry-says/0000018b-3ec5-dcae-afaf-7eff6ef70000</link>